\id EPH - Tuivang Holy Bible
\h EFESA
\toc1 Ephesa
\toc2 Ephesa
\toc3 Efes
\mt1 EPHESA
\c 1
\s1 Zeelawi
\p 
\v 1 Khawsa ngaihnaak amyihna Jesu Khrih a ceityih pynoet na ak awm, Paul ing, Ephesa khaw awhkaw thlakciim, Khrih awh ypawm na ak awm thlangkhqi venawh.
\v 2 Ni Pa Khawsa ingkaw Bawipa Jesu Khrih a venna kaw qeennaak awm seh nyng.
\s1 Khrih-awh Myihla Zoseennaak
\p 
\v 3 Ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih Khawsa ingkaw Pa venawh kyihcahnaak awm seh, khawk khan awh ningnih ce amah ing zoseennaak ni pek khqi nawh Khrih awh Myihla ben zoseennaak soepkep ce ni pek khqi hawh hy.
\v 4 Ak ciimcaih coet a kap kaana a haiawh awm aham khawmdek a syn hlan awhkawng ningnih ce nik tyk khqi hawh hy. Lungnaak awh
\v 5 amah ing ningnih ve a cana taak aham Jesu Khrih awh a oepchoeh na ni hoep khqi hawh hy, amah a zeelnaak ingkaw ngaihnaak amyihna –
\v 6 a boeimang qeennaak kyihcahnaak ingkaw, amah ing a lungnaak thlang awh ningnih ce a zoe na ni pek khqi hawh hy.
\v 7 A thi ak caming thawngnaak ce ni hu uhy, thawlh qeenkhaw ngainaak, ak dung soeih soeih Khawsam qeennaak amyihna,
\v 8 ningnih ak khanawh cyihnaak ingkaw zaksimnaak ce a hai kaana ni vyih sih khqi hy.
\v 9 Amah a koe ak leek zeelnaak, Khrih awh ang cainaak a awm hawh amyihna, amah awhkaw ang hyp ngaihnaak ce ningnih a venawh dang sak hawh hy,
\v 10 a tym a khoek awh khan ing khawmdek awhkaw ik-oeih boeih boeih a lu na ak awm Khrih ak kaina taak peek boeih aham ak kawngaih na awm hawh hy.
\p 
\v 11 Amah awh ningnih awm tyk na ni awm uhy, amah a ngaihnaak amyihna ik-oeih boeih ak poekkung ing ang cainaak amyihna ni hoep oepchoeh khqi hawh hy.
\v 12 A boeimangnaak ak kyihcahkung na ni awmnaak thai aham, ningnih taw Khrih awh ngaih-unaak ak ta cyk na ni awm uhy.
\v 13 Nangmih awm awitak, ni loetnaak awithang leek ce naming zaak awh, Khrih awh awm hawh lawt uhyk ti. Namik cangnaak hawh a dawngawh, nangmih a pum awh hatnaak, Ciim Myihla awikamnaak ce awm hawh hy.
\v 14 Khawsa koena ak awm amah a boeimangnaak kyihcah aham ak awmkhqi a thaawngnaak a pha hlan dy ningnih a qo pangnaak hly awh anih ce hawih na awm hy.
\s1 Zeelawi Kqawn Ingkaw Cykcahnaak
\p 
\v 15 Vawh, nangmih ing Bawipa Jesu awh cangnaak ing thlakciimkhqi boeih nami lungnaak ce kang zaak awh,
\v 16 a boet kaana zeelnaak awi kqawn nyng, kak cykcahnaak awh nangmih ce ni sim khqi poepa nyng.
\v 17 Ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih a Khawsa, qeennaak ing ak be Pa ing cyihnaak Myihla ing amah ce ak leek bet na nami sim thainaak aham ingkaw huh saknaak ce a ni peek thainaak khqi aham thoeh poepa nyng.
\v 18 Amah ing anik khynaak ngaih-unaak, thlakciimkhqi ing boeimangnaak qo pang hly kawi ce nami sim thainaak aham nangmih ak kawlung mik a dai sak naak aham cykcah bai nyng.
\v 19 Ak cangnaak ningnih boeih aham thaawmnaak ak bau soeih ce awm hy. Cawhkaw thaawmnaak cetaw ak thaawmnaak ak bau soeih ing bibi amyihna awm hy.
\s1 Khrih-awh Khawsa A Saithainaak
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Sam 110.1.\x*Khrih ce thawh tlaih nawh Khawk khan hun awh Pa tang benawh ang ngawihsaknaak thaawmnaak ce haw nahy,
\v 21 uknaak ingkaw saithainaak, thaawmnaak ingkaw temnaak, peek thai na ak awm ming boeih boeih, tuh a khuk awh am nawh ak law hly a khuk ak khanawh Khrih taw awm hy.
\v 22 Ik-oeih boeih boeih a khawk kaiawh Khawsa ing taak pe nawh thlangboel aham ik-oeih boeih boeih a lu na anih ce tahy.
\v 23 Cawhkaw thlangboel cetaw a pumsa ni, ik-oeih soepkep awh ak be soep saknaak ce.
\c 2
\s1 Thihnaak Awkawng Hqingnaak
\p 
\v 1 Nangmih taw, awi eeknaak ingkaw thawlhnaak awh thi hawh uhyk ti.
\v 2 Ve khawmdek a phung na nami awm awh ce zilh ak ukkung boei, tuh awm awi amak ngaikhqi venawh bi ak bi myihla a phungna awm uhyk ti.
\v 3 Ak kqym awh ningnih boeih awm cekkhqing lakawh khaw ni sa lawt uhy. Thawlh a ngaih sainaak ingkaw thawlh ngaihnaak a huawh ce ning bat lawt uhy. Thlak changkhqi amyihna, ningnih awm kawsonaak ak zawkkhqi na ni awm uhy.
\v 4 Cehlai ningnih a ni lungnaak khqi soeih a dawngawh, qeennaak ing ak be, Khawsa ing,
\v 5 awi eeknaak awh ni thih huiawh awm Khrih ing ningnih ce ni hqing sak khqi haih tlaih hawh hy – qeennaak awh ni nangmih hulna ni awm uh.
\v 6 Khawsa ing ningnih ve Khrih ing ni thawh sak khqi haih nawh, Khrih awh khan hun na amah ing ning ngawih sak khqi haih hy.
\v 7 Ak law hly khuk a awm awh am qeennaak amni nyhtah thai noeng ce ang dang saknaak aham ingkaw Jesu Khrih awh ningnih ani lungnaak khqi ce ang dang saknaak ahamni.
\v 8 Caangnaak caming qeenaak awh thaawngna namik awm ni; namimah a bibi camawh am nawh, Khawsa a them pek ni;
\v 9 bibinaak ak caming amni, cemyih am kaa taw thlang ing cawng a cah qu kawm uh.
\v 10 Them leek sai ahamna Isu Khrih awh saina ni awm nawh amak a kut sai qoena nik awm ni; ce them leek sai ce ni khawsak hly qoena Khawsa ing a syn qoe ni.
\s1 Khrih-awh Pynoet
\p 
\v 11 Cedawngawh, maana ningnih pumsa awh Gentel, pumsa awh kut ing sai “Chahhui qeet” ami tikhqi ingkaw “Chahhui amak qeet” ami tikhqi aw,
\v 12 ce tloek awhce, Khrih kana, Israelkhqi a tui khaw ingqaw lak hla ing, khawmdek awh ve ngaih-uunaak amak ta ingkaw Khawsa kana awm ing, awikam awhkawng khinna nami awm ce sim poe kawm uk ti.
\v 13 Cehlai tuh awhtaw Jesu Khrih awh, nangmih maana ak hla soeihna namik awmkhqi ce Khrih a thi ing zoei sak awm uhyk ti.
\p 
\v 14 Amah qoe qoe ce ningnih aham qoepnaak na awm hawh hy, anih ing pakkhih ce pynoet na sai nawh qaal anglak pheknaak vawng ak awm ce hqe hawh hy,
\v 15 a pumsa ing anaa ak awipeek sai aham ak awmkhqi boeih ce hqe hawh hy. Amah awh thlang pakkhih ak khuiawh kawng thlak thai pynoet sai aham cai hy, cemyihna qoepnaak ce sai hy.
\v 16 Vawhkaw pum pynoet awhkawng thinglam ak caming Khawsa ingkaw cekqawi anglak law awh tuqunaak ce sai hy, thinglam awh a thihnaak ak caming qaal qunaak ce boet sak hy.
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Is. 57.19.\x*Nangmih ak hla nakaw ak awmkhqi ingkaw ak zoe awh ak awmkhqi venna law nawh qoepnaak awi ce kqawn hy.
\v 18 Cedawngawh amah ak caming ningnih boeih ing Pa a venawh Ciim Myihla pynoet ak caming tuqunaak ce ni ta uhy.
\p 
\v 19 Cedawngawh, nangmih taw khawlawng thlang ingkaw thlang lang na am awm voel uhyk ti, Khawsa ak thlangkhqi ingkaw Khawsa ipkhui cakaw na awm hawh uhyk ti.
\v 20 Ceityihkhqi ingkaw tawnghakhqi awh sak na awm u tiksaw, Khrih amah qoe qoe ce a kil awhkaw lungkhoeng na awm hy.
\v 21 Anih awh im ce tuqu boeih nawh Bawipa a bawkim na dyi hy.
\v 22 Nangmih awm amah awhce Myihla-awh, Khawsa awmnaak a ham sakna namik awm ni.
\c 3
\s1 Gentelkhqi Venawh Paul A Bibi
\p 
\v 1 Cedawngawh kai Paul, nangmih Gentelkhqi ak camawh Jesu Khrih awh thawng ak tla, ing –
\v 2 nangmih aham kai a venawh peek na ak awm Khawsa am qeennaak bibi ka taak ce za hawh uhyk ti;
\v 3 cemyihna awihyp ce ak tawi cana ka qee law hawh amyihna kai a venawh awiphawngnaak ing ni sim sak hy.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Kol 1.26,27.\x*Ce ak awi ce nami noet awh, Khrih ak awihyp ka huhnaak akawng ce zasim thai kawm uk ti,
\v 5 cawhkaw awihyp ce tuh Myihla ing Khawsa a ceityih ciimkhqi ingkaw tawnghakhqi venawh ang dang sak amyihna ak chang cadil khqi anglaklung awh simsak na am awm hy.
\v 6 Cetaw veni, Awithang leek ak caming Jesu Khrih-awh Gentelkhqi qo a pangpyikhqi, pumsa a ke a baipyikhqi, awikam dopyikhqi na awm uhy.
\v 7 Amah a saithainaak bibinaak ak caming ka venawh peek na ak awm Khawsam qeennaak awh kai taw ve awithang leek a tamnaa na awm nyng.
\p 
\v 8 Khawsak thlangkhqi boeih ak khuiawh ak zawi soeihkhqi anglakawh zawi khqoet hlai nyng vawhkaw am qeennaak ve ka venawh ni pehy: Gentelkhqi venawh am sui thai noengna ak awm Khrih a boeinaak ce kqawn peek aham ingkaw,
\v 9 maa awh, ik-oeih boeih ak synkung Khawsa awh thuh na ak awm, ve awihyp a bibinaak ve thlang boeih a venawh sim sak aham ni.
\v 10 Anih angcainaak taw, thlangboel ak caming, Khawsa a cyihnaak ak dung soeih ce khawk khan hun awhkaw ukkungkhqi ingkaw saithainaak ak takhqi venawh simsak aham ni,
\v 11 amah a kumqui angcainaak ce ningnih Bawipa Jesu Khrih awh soep sak hawh hy.
\v 12 Amah awh cangnaak ak caming ngaihdingnaak ingkaw ypnaak taak doena Khawsa venawh ni zoe thai hawh uhy.
\v 13 Cedawngawh, nangmih boeimangnaak aham kai ing ka khuikhanaak awh ve namik tha koeh set sak uh.
\s1 Myihla Thamahnaak Ham Cykcahnaak
\p 
\v 14 Ve ak camawh Pa a haiawh khuk sym ing koep nyng,
\v 15 anih a venawh kawng khawk khan ingkaw khawmdek awh ak awm a cakaw khqi ing a mimah ang ming ce hu uhy.
\v 16 A boeimangnaak ingkaw ang Myihlaa ak caming nangmih ak kawlung khuiawh thaawmnaak ani peeknaak khqi thai aham cykcah lah uh,
\v 17 nangmih ak kawlung khuiawh cangnaak ak caming Khrih a awm thainaak aham. Lungnaak awh namik kqa thla unawh nami caknaak aham cykcah nyng.
\v 18 Thlakcimkhqi mi kutoetna a kaunaak, a saunaak, a saangnaak ingkaw a dungnaak khqi ce simcaihthainaak ingkaw,
\v 19 Khrih a lungnaak am sim noeng simthainaak ce ta thai kawm uk ti.
\v 20 Cawhce, ningnih awh ak bi themsaithainaak amyihna, ni thoehnaak ingkaw nik poeknaak boeih anglakawh ak saang soeihna them ak saithaikung venawh,
\v 21 kumqui dy, kumqui dy na, thlangboelkhqi ingkaw Khrih Jesu awh boeimangnaak awm poe seh nyng. Amen.
\c 4
\s1 Khrih A Pumqaw Ingkaw A Ke A Bai
\p 
\v 1 Nangmih ing khynaak nami huh amyihna khynaak ing ang qoep na khaw nami sak aham Bawipa awh thawng ak tla kai ing ni yyn khqi nyng.
\v 2 Namik kaw dung sak unawh taw awm moel moel uh; yhnaak ta law unawh taw pynoet ingkaw pynoet kawdung doena lungnaak ing awm law uh.
\v 3 Qoepnaak ing pinzen qu unawh Myihla ak kawdawnaak ce nami hamnaak thai ham tha lo lah uh.
\v 4 Pum pynoet doeng awm nawh Myihla awm pynoet ni a awm – nangmih anik khy khqi awh ngaih-unaak pynoet doeng ing a nik khy khqi amyihna –
\v 5 Bawipa pynoet, cangnaak pynoet, baptisma pynoet;
\v 6 ik-oeih soepkep ak khan ingkaw ik-oeih soepkep awh ak awm Pa Khawsa pynoet doeng ni a awm.
\p 
\v 7 Cehlai ningnih boeih a venawh Khrih ing a hoep lawnaak amyihna am qeennaak ce peek na awm hawh hy.
\v 8 Cedawngawh:
\q1 “Khan na a hang kaiawh tamnaakhqi ce sawi khqi nawh,
\q2 thlanghqingkhqi venawh awm kutdo ce pe hy,” tinawh anak kqawn hy.
\m 
\v 9 (Amah ce khawmdek ak kaina, khawmdek awh nuk kqum hy ti am awhtaw “hang kaai hy” tive ikaw ak kqawn ngaihnaak hy voei?
\v 10 A nuk kqum ce khawk khan boeih ak khanna a hak kaai ceni, khawmdek ingkaw khawnghi boeih anih ing a khuk thainaak aham cemyihna ce awm hy.)
\v 11 Anih ing thlangvang ce ceityih na, thlang vang ce tawngha na, thlangvang ce awithang leek ak kqawnkung na, thlangvang ce tuuk khai ingkaw cawngpyikung na tahy,
\v 12 Khawsa ak thlangkhqi ing bibi thai unawh, Khrih a pum ce a ming dyih naak sak thai aham,
\v 13 cangnaak awh pynoet na bawngqu unawh Khawsa Capa simnaak awh kawcyihnaak taak dyna ni awmnaak aham ingkaw, Khrih awh ni beenaak thai aham cemyihna ce tahy.
\v 14 Cawhtaw naasen na amni awm voel kawm uh, tuinu ing hu na hai na amni khyn voel kawmsaw, cawngpyinaak ingkaw thlang a thainaak soepkep ing hu na hai na amni zawn voel kaw.
\v 15 Lungnaak ingkaw awitak ce nik kqawn kawm usaw, lu na ak awm Khrih awh ik-oeih soepkep awh ning taai hawh kawm uh.
\v 16 Amah a venawh kawng pum boeih ce tuqu nawh tha pe qu uhy, lungnaak ing taai unawh, amah a bi ce bi qip uhy.
\s1 Dainaak Cakhqi Myihna Khawsak
\p 
\v 17 Cedawngawh ve ve ka nik kqawn peek khqi, ve a dawngawh Bawipa awh awm unawh, kawna amak nyt Gentelkhqi ak poeknaak amyihna nami awm aham am awm voel hy.
\v 18 A mingmih ang zaksimnaak taw khaw amyihna than nawh, simnaak a taak kaana kawlung ami qil sak adawngawh Khawsa hqingnaak ingqawi phek qu uhy.
\v 19 Ak che ak leek simnaak a taak voel kaa qoena, pumsa ngaih amak ciimcaih soepkep benawh a mimah ingkaw a mimah ce pe qu uhy, hyy ngaihnaak benawh cet khqoet khqoet uhy.
\p 
\v 20 Cehlai, nangmih taw, cemyihna Khrih ce am sim uhyk ti.
\v 21 Anih akawng ce naming zaaknaak amyihna Jesu Khrih awh ak awm awitak ce nangmih a venawh cawngpyi na awm hawh hy.
\v 22 Maa nakaw nami khawsaknaak thlanghqing khym, thailatnaak ing ak bee ce khawng unawh,
\v 23 namik kawlung ce myihla awhce ak thaaina awm unawh;
\v 24 thlanghqing ak thaai, awitak dyngnaak ingkaw cimcaihnaak awh Khawsamyihna saina ak awm ing ce thoeihcam qu kawm uk ti.
\p 
\v 25 Cedawngawh nangmih boeih ing amak thym ik-oeih ce suut unawh na kengsam awhkaw thlang a venawh awih thym ce namik kqawn aham awm hy, ningnih ve pum pynoet a ke a baikhqi na ni awm uhy.
\v 26 Kawso unawh, thawlh mah koeh sai uh; namik kawsonaak ce khaw ing koeh tlaak pyi seh;
\v 27 setan ce ang dyih hun koeh pe law uh.
\v 28 Ak qu khawi ing koeh qu voel seh, bibi seitaw, ak voet ak hlauh thlangkhqi ce a do a dan thainaak aham amah a kut qoe ing amah aham a hawihkhangnaak hly bi ce sai seh.
\p 
\v 29 Nam khak khuiawh kawng awihche koeh cawn sak, cehlai a ngoengaihnaak amyihna themleek ak sai ham awileek a hoei cawn seh, ak ngai zaakhqi ham lungnaakna a awmnaak a hamna.
\v 30 Khawsa a Ciim Myihla ce koeh kawseet sak uh, hulnaak nyn aham anih awhce hatnaak deng sihna namik awm ni.
\v 31 Awihkhaakhqi, kawsonaakkhqi, kawtawinaakkhqi, qawnaakkhqi, awihche kqawnnaakkhqi boeih boeih ingkaw thawlhnaak boeih boeih khqi ce centaak kawm uk ti.
\v 32 Pynoet ingkaw pynoet ak khanawh qeennaak ta law unawh, Khrih awh Khawsa ing nangmih qeenkhaw a ning ngai pekkhqi amyihna, nangmih pynoet ingkaw pynoet qeenkhaw ngai qu lah uh.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 A lungnaak a cakhqi na nami awm amyihna, Khawsa a khawboe ak oetkung na awm law lah uh,
\v 2 Khrih ing ningnih ni lung nak khqi nawh ningnih aham Khawsa venawh bawktui bulnaak na ang peek qu amyihna, nangmih awm lungnaak ing khaw sa lah uh.
\v 3 Nangmih anglakawh nu ingkaw pa thawlhnaak, kamvaanaak ingkaw amak ciimcaih ikawmyih awm a awm qoe qoe aham am awm hy, vemyihkhqi ve Khawsa thlangkhqi ing am kawih na uhy.
\v 4 Chahnaak ben awihkqawn khqi, qawnaak awihkqawnkhqi ingkaw amak coeng poeloem halang awihkqawnkhqi ve a awm voel kaana zeelawi mah kqawn kawm uk ti.
\v 5 Vekkhqi ve sim kawm uk ti: khawboe amak leek, amak caih ik-oeih ingkaw ak kamvaa ak thlang cemyih ak thlang taw myihlip ak bawk ak thlang ni – cemyih ak thlang ing Khrih ingkaw Khawsa qam ce am pang thai kaw.
\s1 Khawkdai Ingkaw Khawmthan
\p 
\v 6 Thlang ing awihqawng ing koeh ni thai nak khqi seh, kawtih cemyihna awi amak ngai thlangkhqi ak khanawh Khawsa ak kawsonaak ce pha kaw.
\v 7 Cemyih ak thlangkhqi mi koeh awm law haih uh.
\v 8 Thannaak ak khuiawh ni nami awm hlai, tuh taw Bawipa awh vangnaak ak khuiawh awm hawh uhyk ti. Cedawngawh vangnaak cakhqi amyihna awm lah uh,
\v 9 (Ikawtih vangnaak ak thaih taw themleek, dyngnaak ingkaw awitak awh awm nawh),
\v 10 Khawsa ngaihnaak ce hu uhy.
\v 11 Ak thaih amak awm than a bibiaak awh koeh thum unawh taw, cemyih ik-oeih sainaakkhqi ce dang sak lat uh.
\v 12 Awingai kaana thannaak ak khui awhkaw ik-oeih sai ve kqawn aham awm chah awm hy.
\v 13 Cehlai vangnaak ing ak coei ik-oeih boeih taw huh thai na awm hy,
\v 14 vangnaak ing ik-oeih boeih ce huh thai aham coei hy, cedawngawh, “Aw ak ip nang, hqyng nawhtaw, thihnaak ak khuiawh kawng tho hlah cawhtaw Khrih a vangnaak ing nik coei kaw,” tinawh anak kqawn hawh hy.
\p 
\v 15 Cedawngawh nami khawsak naak awh ce ak nep na naming ngaih ta lah uh, a cyih amak awm amyihna koeh awm unawh thlakcyi amyihna awm lah uh,
\v 16 khawnghikhqi ve ama leekvoel hawh adawngawh, a tym leek boeih boeih ce thlai lah uh.
\v 17 Cedawngawh thlakqaw amyihna koeh awm unawh taw, Bawipa ak kawngaih ve ikawnu tice sim law lah uh.
\v 18 Zuu koeh qui uh, ce ing khawboe amak leek ce awm sak hy. Ce anglak awh Myihla ing be lah uh.
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Kol 3.16,17.\x*Pynoet ingkaw pynoet Saam awi kqawn unawh, kyihcahnaak laa ingkaw Myihla ben laa ce sa lah uh. Namik kawk khuiawh Bawipa venawh kyihcahnaak laa ce sa lah uh,
\v 20 a soep hoeiawh Pa Khawsa venawh ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih ang ming ing zeelawi kqawn poepa lah uh.
\v 21 Khrih kqihchahnaak ing pynoet ingkaw pynoet pe qu lah uh.
\s1 Chungvaa Khawsak
\p 
\v 22 Zukhqi, Bawipa venawh naming peek qu amyihna nami vaakhqi venawh pe qu lah uh.
\v 23 Khrih taw amah a pumna ak awm, amah ing a thaawng thlangboel a lu na a awm amyihna, vaa taw zu a lu na awm hy.
\v 24 Thlangboel ing Khrih a venawh ang peek qu amyihna, zukhqi ingawm ik-oeih soepkep awh vaakhqi venawh ang peek qu aham awm hy.
\p 
\v 25 Vaakhqi, Khrih ing a thlangboel lungna nawh a hqingnaak a peek amyihna, nami zukhqi ce lung law na uh.
\v 26 Khrih ing thlangboel ce ciimcaih sak hy, awi ak caming tui ing sil nawh,
\v 27 amah a venawh ak vang thlangboel, myn a maa amak kap qoe, ak ciimcaih ingkaw coet amak kap na a peek amyihna nami zuukhqi ce lung law na lah uh.
\v 28 Cemyih lawtna, vaakhqi ing ami zuukhqi ce a mimah a pum ami lungnaak lawt amyihna ami lungnaak aham awm hy. A zu ak lungnaak thlang taw amah a pum ak lungnaak thlang ni.
\v 29 U ingawm amah a pum ce am sawh na khawi hy, Khrih ing thlangboel a hquisawi amyihna, hqin amcah nawh hqui a sawi hy –
\v 30 ningnih taw amah a pum awhkaw a ke a baikhqi na nik awm ni.
\v 31 Ve ak camawh pa ing a nu ingkaw a pa cehta nawh a zu ce tawm kawm saw, pakkhih ce pumoet na coeng hawh kawm nih.
\v 32 Ve ve awihdung awihyp na awm hy; cehlai kai ing kak kqawn taw Khrih ingkaw thlangboel akawng ni kak kqawn hy.
\v 33 Cehlai, nangmih boeih ing nami mah a pum nami lungnaak amyihna nami zukhqi ce nami lungnaak aham awm hy, zukhqi ingawm a mi vaakhqi ce a mik kqihchah aham awm hy.
\c 6
\s1 Cakhqi Ingkaw Nupakhqi
\p 
\v 1 Naasenkhqi, Bawipa awh nami nu ingkaw nami pakhqi ak awi ce ngai uh; vetaw ak dyng na awm hy.
\v 2 “Nanu ingkaw napa kqihchah lah,” tinaak awi ve awipeek lammacyk ni.
\v 3 “Naham na leek nawh khawmdek awh na hqinglu sang kaw,” tinaak awitaak ak awm ni.
\v 4 Pakhqi, nami cakhqi kawsonaak hly kawi koeh sai law pe uh; ce anglakawhtaw Bawipa awh yyn a tawnnaak ingkaw cuk am kiknaak ing taai law sak lah uh.
\s1 Tamnaa Ingkaw Boei
\p 
\v 5 Tamnaakhqi, Khrih ak awi naming ngai peek amyihna, khawmdek awhkaw nami boeikhqi ak awi ce kawlung ciimnaak ing ngaih law pe unawh taw kqihnaak ing kqihchah lah uh.
\v 6 Thlanghqing kawzeelnaak hamna mik huh doengawh bi a sai kana, Khrih a tamnaa na nami awm amyihna, namik kawlung khuiawh kawng Khawsa ak kawngaih ce sai law uh.
\v 7 Thlanghqing a bi ak bi amyihna ak poek kaana, Bawipa bi ak bi amyihna, namik kawlung tang tang ing bibi law pe uh,
\v 8 kawtih tamnaa awm tamnaa am awm, thlang boeih ing bibi leek ami bi amyihna, Bawipa ing kutdo ce pe kaw, tice sim uhyk ti.
\p 
\v 9 Boeikhqi, nangmih ingawm nami tamnaakhqi ce cemyihna sai law lawt uh. Cekkhqi ingkaw nami Bawipa taw khawk khan na awm hy tice sim doena, tamnaakhqi ce koeh the koeh kha na uh, kawtih Khawsa ing u a haai awm am toek hy.
\s1 Khrihca Ingkaw Myihla Phuqhaa
\p 
\v 10 A hukhit awh, Bawipa a saithai thaawmnaak awh namik tha awm law sak lah uh.
\v 11 Setan ang cainaak ce nami khamnaak thai aham Khawsa a phuqhaa ing thoeihcam qu lah uh.
\v 12 Ikawtih ningnih taw pumsa thisa qaal mi amning tuk qu unawh, ukkungkhqi, saithainaak ak takhqi, ve khawmdek than thaawmnaakkhqi ingkaw khan nakaw Setan myihla thaawmnaakkhqi mi ni ning tuk qu uh.
\v 13 Cedawngawh Khawsa ang thoeihcamnaak Phuqhaa ing thoeihcam qu lah uh, cawh ni khawnghi amak nep a pha law awh, ak cakna dyi thai kawm u tiksaw, ik-oeih boeih nami sai coeng dyna naming dyih hly thai hy.
\v 14 Cedawngawh awitak cawi zeennaak ing zeen qu unawh, dyngnaak kqangdan ing dah qu doena,
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Is. 52.7.\x*qoepnaak awithang leek khawmyk ce myk doena a oepchoeh na awm lah uh.
\v 16 Vemyihkhqi boeih boeih coengawh, cangnaak phuhqa ce pawm lah uh, ve ing ni setan a la ak alh hlap hlap ce namim thih hly thai hy.
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Is. 59.17.\x*Hulnaak thi lumyk ce myk unawh, Khawsa a zawzi Myihlak zawzi ce pawm lah uh.
\v 18 A soep hoeiawh cykcahnaak thoehnaak soepkep ing Myihla awh cykcah lah uh. Ve ve nak kawk khuiawh taak doena, thlakciimkhqi boeih aham cykcah poe lah uh.
\p 
\v 19 Ityk awhawm kam kha ka awng hoeiawh awithang leek awihyp ve ak kqih kaana kak kqawnnaak thai aham, kai aham awm cykcah law lah uh,
\v 20 ve a dawngawh dyihthing na awm nyng saw thiqui ing khihna awm nyng. Kqihnaak a taak kaana kak kqawnnaak thai aham, cykcah law uh.
\s1 Hukhit Awiyynnaak
\p 
\v 21 Ka lungnaak ka naa, Bawipa a ypawm tyihzawih, Tukika ing ik-oeih soepkep ce nik kqawn law pek khqi bit kaw, cawhkaw iamyihna ka awm nawh ikaw ka sai tice sim kawm uk ti.
\v 22 Ikawmyihna ka mi awm tice sim unawh anih ing tha ani peeknaakkhqi thai aham anih ce tyi law kawng.
\v 23 Pa Khawsa ingkaw Bawipa Jesu Khrih a ven awhkaw lungnaak ingkaw cangnaak ce koeinaakhqi venawh awm seh nyng.
\v 24 Amak thi thai lungnaak ing ni Bawipa Jesu Khrih ak lungnaak khqi ak khanawh am qeennaak awm seh nyng. 
